               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Dǝrsāna Mikāʾel, Homiliary for the feasts of St Michael (fols.
                     5ra-121va)
 I-1) Homily by Athanasius [Timothy], Patriarch of Alexandria
                     for the 12th of Ḫǝdār (fols. 5ra-13rb); miracle (fols. 13rb-15ra);
                     commemorative notice (fols. 15ra-17rb); ʾarke-hymn (fol. 17rb)
 I-2) Homily
                     by an anonymous author for Tāḫśāś (fols. 17va-24rb); miracle (fols. 24rb-26va);
                     commemorative notice (fols. 25va-26rb); ʾarke-hymn (fol. 26rb) 
 I-3)
                     Homily [by Epiphanius, Metropolitan of Cyprus] for Ṭǝrr (fols. 26va-37rb);
                     miracle (fols. 37rb-38rb); commemorative notice (fol. 38rb-va); ʾarke-hymn
                     (fol. 38va-vb) 
 I-4) Homily by an anonymous author for Yakkātit (fols.
                     38vb-42va); miracle (fols. 42va-43vb); commemorative notice (fol. 44ra-vb);
                     ʾarke-hymn (fol. 44va-vb) 
 I-5) Homily by [Severus], Metropolitan
                     [Patriarch] of Antiochia for the 12th of Maggābit (fols. 45ra-63va); miracle
                     (fols. 63va-65ra); commemorative notice (fol. 65ra-rb); ʾarke-hymn (fol.
                     65rb-va) 
 I-6) Homily by [Metropolitan Yoḥannǝs the Orthodox] for Miyāzyā
                     (fols. 65va-70vb); miracle (fols. 70vb-73ra); commemorative notice (fol.
                     73ra-va); ʾarke-hymn (fol. 73va-vb) 
 I-7) Homily by Yoḥannǝs, Metropolitan
                     of Ethiopia for Gǝnbot (fols. 73vb-75ra); miracle (fols. 75vb-76vb, 87ra-va);
                     commemorative notice (fols. 87va-88ra); ʾarke-hymn (fol. 88ra) 
 I-8)
                     Homily by [Yoḥannǝs], Metropolitan of ʾAksum for [Sane] (fol. 88rb-94vb,
                     77ra-vb); miracle (fols. 77vb-79ra); commemorative notice (fols. 79ra-86va);
                     ʾarke-hymn (fol. 86va-vb) 
 I-9) Homily [by Metropolitan Yoḥannǝs] for
                     Ḥamle (fols. 95ra-100rb); miracle (fols. 100rb-101rb); commemorative notice
                     (fol. 101rb-vb); ʾarke-hymn (fol. 101vb) 
 I-10) Homily by an anonymous
                     author for Naḥāse (fols. 102ra-105vb); miracle (fols. 105vb-106vb);
                     commemorative notice (fols. 106vb-107ra); ʾarke-hymn (fol. 107ra-rb) 
                     I-11) Homily by an anonymous author for Maskaram (fols. 108ra-111ra); miracle
                     (fols. 111rb-113vb)
 I-12) Homily by an anonymous author for Ṭǝqǝmt (fols.
                     114ra-118va); miracle (fols. 118va-120vb); commemorative notice (fols.
                     120vb-121va); ʾarke-hymn (fol. 121va) 
 
 Additiones 1-3.</summary>
