                  <additions>
                     <list>
                        <item xml:id="a1">
                           <locus target="#107rb">f. 107rb</locus>
                           <desc>: Donation note.</desc>
                           <quote xml:lang="gez"/>
                           <quote xml:lang="en"/> The note states that the Ms. was purchased and
                           donated to the church by ʾabuna Gabra Mikāʾel. It mentions also his
                           family members: his father ʾabuna<note> Walda Śǝllāse, mother ʿUṣǝftä
                              Dǝngǝl, wife Walatta Ḥǝywat, son Walda Mikāʾel and his sisters Ḫāyla
                              Mikāʾel, Walatta Mikāʾel, Walatta Kidān. </note>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a2">
                           <locus target="#113vb">f. 113vb</locus>
                           <desc>: Commemorative notice for the 12th of Maskaram and
                              ʾarke-hymn.</desc>
                           <quote xml:lang="gez"/>
                           <quote xml:lang="en"/>
                           <note> The omitted commemorative notice and hymn are written in smaller,
                              compressed script. </note>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a3">
                           <locus target="#121vb">f. 121vb</locus>
                           <desc>: Donation note.</desc>
                           <quote xml:lang="gez"/>
                           <quote xml:lang="en"/>
                           <note> The note has been washed out, but the names of ʾArkä Sǝllus and
                              his wife Walatta Māryām can still be read. </note>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="e1">- Smaller script is used on <locus from="106vb" to="107ra">106vb-107ra</locus>, 120-121va.
 - A text, probably written in
                           the same hand as Additio 3, has been erased: <locus target="#122ra">122ra-</locus>vb, 123rb.
 - Crude drawings: <locus from="122v" to="123v">122v-123v</locus>.
 - Crude notes: <locus target="#28r">28r</locus>, 102ra, 123r.</item>
                        <item xml:id="e2">
